Privacy Policy — WealthFolio
Last updated: 28 June 2026
WealthFolio ("the app") is an offline-first portfolio, dividend and capital-gains
tracker for the Pakistan Stock Exchange. This policy explains exactly what data
the app handles.
What we store
Your portfolio data — trades, dividends, cash flows, watchlist, prices and
settings — is stored only on your device. We do not have a server that
receives or holds this data by default.
Data we do not collect
We do not collect personal identifiers, contacts, location, advertising IDs
or device fingerprints.
The app contains no ads, no analytics and no third-party trackers.
No account is required to use the app.
Internet use
The app works fully offline. It connects to the internet only for two optional
features:
Live share prices. When you open the Holdings tab or tap refresh, the app
requests current prices from the public Pakistan Stock Exchange data portal
(`dps.psx.com.pk`). Only public market prices are fetched; no personal data is
sent.
Cloud Backup & Sync (optional). If — and only if — you choose to sign in,
the app uses Supabase to store a backup of your portfolio under your account:
We process the email address you sign up with (for authentication).
We store a copy of your portfolio data so you can sync it across your
devices.
This data is protected so that only your authenticated account can read or
write it. You can delete it at any time by signing in and removing your
backup, or by deleting your account.
If you never sign in, no data ever leaves your device.
Data sharing
We do not sell or share your data with any third party. The only processors
involved are the services you explicitly use: the PSX data portal (public prices)
and Supabase (only if you enable Cloud Sync).
Data retention & deletion
On-device data is removed when you uninstall the app or use the in-app reset.
Cloud backups (if you created any) remain until you delete them or your account.
Children
The app is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect data
from them.
Disclaimer
All figures (returns, dividends, capital gains and tax estimates) are for your
information only and are not financial, tax or investment advice.
